original_title: Outdoors with T.K. and Mike: Turkey Huntin'
overview: TK and Mike enlist the help of pro turkey hunter Eddie Salter who didn't realize what he was getting into.
tagline: A big glass of milk and a bowl full of cobbler...Sit back and relax as we bust us a gobbler.
title: Outdoors with T.K. and Mike: Turkey Huntin'
